 Costruzioni, per descrivere e interpretare il meccanismo di composizione da un punto di vista sia formale sia semantico. Il volume è corredato di un’appendice in cui sono riportati i composti analizzati e i dati quantitativi relativi alle frequenze.  aThis volume provides a detailed overview of compounding in Italian, from the earliest stages until today. Based on an analysis of data from different corpora, it describes the compound words that Italian has created in the course of the centuries, highlighting elements of continuity with Latin as well as innovative aspects.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Italian.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 0aItalian languagexMorphology. 4aDiachronie. 4aKomposition. 4aKonstruktionsmorphologie. 4aWortbildung. 7aFOREIGN LANGUAGE STUDY / Italian.2bisacsh  aWord formation.  acompounding.  aconstruction morphology.  adiachrony.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Linguistics 2020z9783110704563oZDB-23-DSP0 cEPUBz97831106522530 cprintz978311065155340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311065216140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110652161423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110652161.jpg  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Ebook Package 2020b2020  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2020  aZDB-23-DSPb2020